name: Lingga - Wetwetwet
description:
Welcoming the Rainy Season. A noodle soup with lots of cabe rawit (cayenne pepper) to the rescue!

Lingga series. A bowl of IGOR (mI-GOReng, instant fried noodles with egg) in a shape of the iconic "penis" bottle opener from Bali. And let's drink all the stories of IGOR life.
